metadata.name: ADDICTED TO BEAUTY
metadata.description:
There’s nothing left anymore
Only past days reflections of superficiality
Distractions from back when I used to care

Stripped away of all the layers
Bathing in soothing simplicity

Now there’s beauty inside
Outside
Everywhere

Addicted to beauty
Now I don’t see the world for what it is
But for what it could be

Addicted to beauty
Too caught up in daydreaming
For this to really be reality



__________________________________________________

This NFT includes the physical knitted sweater as well as the 1/1 hand embroidered balaclava mask you see in the video.
